  "texts": [
    "That is, abnormalities in the signals were shared between lesioned and unaffected regions.",
    "We also compared the properties of the BOLD signal inside the tumor with the same regions in healthy subjects.",
    "Alterations in lesioned areas were observable in the power of the signal (P j j > 0, p = 0.031, df = 23, one-tailed t-test) but they were significantly more pronounced in the dynamics (Fig. 2e; DAS j j> 0, p < 0.001, df = 23 one-tailed t-test).",
    "1 | sub-PAT07 Edema and DMN functional signals.",
    "a Mean functional signal (BOLD) measured inside the edema of a patient (red) as compared to signals from the same region in healthy subjects (gray)."
